          "summary": "DeepSeek融资条款揭示投资人不投票、资本不参与决策的新模式。AI公司正在用不同方式重新定义「谁有权决定AI往哪里走」，这是比技术路线更深层的竞争。",
          "summary_en": "DeepSeek's financing terms reveal a new model where investors have no voting rights and capital doesn't participate in decisions. AI companies are redefining 'who has the right to decide where AI goes' in different ways.",
